Subject: Web Site not working
Description: After in-place upgrade from 2012R2 to 2016, everything is working accept the access tab on the website. Attaching a screen shot of the error message. It is a generic 503.
Solution_Comment__c:
We reviewed the config file in today's meeting and noticed it was corrupted.
We uninstalled AIC and installed the newest version of the Access Information Center.
After reinstalling the AIC, the customer was able to load it through the access tab from the Report page.
